06:00.403 --> 06:02.710
No definitive answer on that.

06:02.710 --> 06:04.451
Excuse me.

06:04.451 --> 06:06.061
Are you hot?

06:06.061 --> 06:07.497
Mmm, mmm!

06:07.497 --> 06:09.369
I don't drink enough water...

06:09.369 --> 06:10.892
just in my--
sorry--day.

06:10.892 --> 06:12.807
How would you say
this is going?

06:12.807 --> 06:15.375
The flop sweats don't really
help her credibility.

06:15.375 --> 06:16.506
It's super unattractive.

06:16.506 --> 06:18.508
<i>Guys, there's no story here.</i>

06:18.508 --> 06:20.554
A story
is when something happens,

06:20.554 --> 06:23.600
and, literally,
nothing has happened.

06:23.600 --> 06:25.428
Man, it's beautiful
up here, huh?

06:25.428 --> 06:26.821
