06:32.392 --> 06:34.524
Oh, my...
- Dad, make it stop!

06:34.524 --> 06:36.091
Boys, back up!
Back up!

06:36.091 --> 06:38.963
This whole thing is just--
it's all smoke and no fire.

06:40.661 --> 06:42.967
<i>In just a short time,
the Payne Wildfire</i>

06:42.967 --> 06:44.360
<i>has scorched
over 10,000 acres</i>

06:44.360 --> 06:46.231
<i>and remains zero percent contained.</i>

06:46.231 --> 06:47.798
Uh, hey, Cyrus,
what happened

06:47.798 --> 06:50.105
to "we stress-tested the pawls,
they can hold the Hydra"?

06:50.105 --> 06:52.150
