into it,

06:59.288 --> 07:00.811
at which point it becomes
an absolute death trap.

07:00.811 --> 07:03.510
Elliot, why you scratching--
what's wrong with your face?

07:03.510 --> 07:05.903
- Ew, is that herpes?
