it at the press conference?

08:03.526 --> 08:05.180
Oh, I-I'm going back
out there?

08:05.180 --> 08:07.530
I mean, Ian can jump in,
if you want.

08:07.530 --> 08:09.097
No. No, no.
No, I've got it.

08:09.097 --> 08:10.490
I loved--I loved it.

08:10.490 --> 08:12.535
