Get--

09:55.682 --> 09:57.597
- Oh, my God.
- Oh, my goodness.

09:57.597 --> 09:58.772
Oh, my God.

09:58.772 --> 10:00.251
Okay, I'll kill
the "Bloomberg" story.

10:00.251 --> 10:02.689
I have dirt on an editor there.
He's a sick pup.

10:02.689 --> 10:04.734
